               <div class="related">
                <h3>
                 Philosophy Faculty (2017-18)
                </h3>
                <div>
                 <div>
                  <p>
                   <em>
                    Front row (from left): Ariela Lazar, Jonathan Lear, Agnes Callard, Kevin Davey, Michael Kremer, Robert Richards, Gabriel Lear; second row: Tom Pashby, Ben Laurence, Dan Brudney, Malte Willer, Martha C. Nussbaum, Raoul Moati; third row: Anubav Vasudevan, Ben Callard, Jason Bridges, Anton Ford; fourth row: David Finkelstein, Matthias Haase, Robert Pippin, Jim Conant, Matt Boyle; sixth row: William Weaver (staff); not pictured: Arnold Davidson, Bart Schultz, Candace Vogler
